        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>No Patient Left Alone Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill requires hospitals, as a condition of Medicare participation, to have certain written policies and procedures that provide for patient visitation rights and to inform patients of such rights, including any applicable restrictions.</p>]]>
